  "prompt": "What are some good and romantic Malayalam songs?",
  "response": "Certainly! Malayalam cinema has a rich collection of romantic songs known for their melodious tunes and heartfelt lyrics. Here are some popular romantic Malayalam songs:\n\n1. **\"Kanninetti Muttathani\"** from the movie *Black* - Sung by P. Jayachandran and K.S. Chithra.\n2. **\"Malare\"** from the movie *Premam* - Sung by Vijay Yesudas.\n3. **\"Thumbi Penne\"** from the movie *Bangalore Days* - Sung by Haricharan.\n4. **\"Poomuthole\"** from the movie *Joseph* - Sung by K.S. Harisankar.\n5. **\"Kathirunnu Kathirunnu\"** from the movie *Ennu Ninte Moideen* - Sung by Shreya Ghoshal.\n6. **\"Ee Puzhayum\"** from the movie *Indian Rupee* - Sung by Shreya Ghoshal and Karthik.\n7. **\"Vijanathayil\"** from the movie *Kerala Cafe* - Sung by Raveendran.\n8. **\"Kaathoram Kaathoram\"** from the movie *Thodasa Room* - Sung by P. Jayachandran.\n9. **\"Olanjali Kuruvi\"** from the movie *1983* - Sung by P. Jayachandran and Vani Jairam.\n10. **\"Doore Doore\"** from the movie *June* - Sung by Malcolm & Shweta Mohan.\n\nThese songs span different eras and styles, highlighting the versatility and emotional depth of Malayalam music. Enjoy listening!",
